      <a href="/tools/aes-encrypt-decrypt" class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 shadow-sm transition hover:bg-indigo-100 hover:text-indigo-700">&#x1F512; AES Encrypt / Decrypt</a>
