      <a href="/tools/sha256-hash-generator" class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 shadow-sm transition hover:bg-indigo-100 hover:text-indigo-700">&#x1F4DD; SHA-256 Hash Generator</a>
